Custom color scheme picker 
Live preview mode 
PDF export capability 
 
Technical requirements: 
PDF generation capability 
Responsive design`,Bgt="Sales pipeline tracker",jgt=`Create a beautiful and well-designed (with lighter and vibrant colors) sales pipeline tracker with the following requirements: 
 
