main for 1 year",g5t="24/7 customer support",v5t="Updated {count} files",b5t="Updated 1 file",y5t="Updating {file}",w5t="Restore this version",E5t="Undo this change",C5t="Restore",_5t="Undo",A5t="Cancel",D5t="Your last change will be <b>permanently deleted</b>. Are you sure you want to continue?",S5t="Your last message will be <b>permanently deleted</b>. Are you sure you want to continue?",k5t="All your messages after this message will be <b>permanently deleted.</b> Are you sure you want to continue?",x5t="All changes made to your website after this message will be <b>permanently deleted.</b> Are you sure you want to continue?",T5t="Don't show this again",I5t="Some files failed to update",O5t="Failed to update files",R5t="Supabase documentation",M5t="Connect Supabase",L5t="Connecting Supabase...",F5t="Please wait until AI is done making changes...",P5t="Connect Supabase project.",N5t="Some errors were found that need fixing.",B5t="Additional errors were found that need fixing.",j5t="Main page",z5t="Preview",$5t="Show errors",U5t="Back to preview",H5t="Error logs",V5t="We've detected errors that need fixing. You can ask Horizons to fix them (uses 1 AI credit).",W5t="Hostinger dashboard",q5t="Duplicate this website",G5t="Export code",Y5t="Share feedback",Z5t="Account sharing",K5t="Share your invite link on socials:",X5t="Build fully functional websites and web apps just by chatting with AI! Get {percentage}% extra discount with my link: {link}",J5t="Edit texts",Q5t="Refresh projects",evt="Publishing can take a couple of minutes. Please wait.",tvt="Save",nvt="Saving",rvt="This text can be changed only through chat.",ovt="Turn off text editing",ivt="Add text",avt="Upgrade & get a gift",svt="We've found an error in your website. Ask Horizons to try and fix it – this will use 1 AI credit",lvt="Something went wrong on our end. This didn't cost you an AI credit.",uvt="We're having trouble loading your website",cvt="Try sending your message again.",dvt="Switch to text editing mode",fvt="Turn off text editing mode",hvt="Integrations",pvt="Add user sign-ups, logins, data storage, and other backend features.",mvt="Manage products, orders, payments, and more with a built-in admin panel – no prompting needed.",gvt="Track how many visitors you get and the top countries they come from.",vvt="Connect online store",bvt="I've disconnected Online Store integration. Please remove all references/imports from my entire codebase where EcommerceApi.js file is used.",yvt="Orders",wvt="Products",Evt="Discounts",Cvt="Categories",_vt="Analytics",Avt="Failed to load analytics",Dvt="Settings",Svt="Disconnect store",kvt="Disconnect online store?",xvt="This means that all the products you’ve added will be deleted from your website, and checkout will stop working. You can reconnect your store anytime.",Tvt="Failed to load store",Ivt="Failed to load website data",Ovt="Failed to disconnect store",Rvt="Failed to create store",Mvt="Online store",Lvt="Failed to create online store",Fvt="Store manager",Pvt="Customers",Nvt="Change image",Bvt="Upload new image",jvt="Edit content",zvt="What is Supabase?",$vt="How do I connect Supabase to my website?",Uvt="Is Supabase free to use?",Hvt="Supabase documentation",Vvt="Supabase adds backend features to your website – like storing data, handling sign-ups and logins, or syncing updates in real time – without you having to build it all from scratch.",Wvt="Think of it as the behind-the-scenes system that powers your website. While Horizons handles what people see (the frontend),  Supabase manages everything in the background (the backend).",qvt="You get all the essentials to make your website run smoothly — so you can focus on building and bringing your ideas to life.",Gvt="To connect Supabase to your website: {0}",Yvt="Click ‘Connect’ above. You’ll be redirected to Supabase, where you can log in to an existing Supabase account or create a new one.",Zvt="Select the organization you want to manage through Horizons. If you don’t have an organization, create one.",Kvt="Once you’re redirected back to Horizons, connect a Supabase project by clicking ‘Connect’. You can also create a new project by clicking ‘Create new project‘.",Xvt="Confirm the connection and wait until everything’s set up. You can track the progress in the chat.",Jvt="Supabase has a free tier, and paid plans are available if you need more resources like storage, bandwidth, or other advanced features.",Qvt="See more information on their {0}.",e3t="pricing page",t3t="If you have any questions about Supabase, {0}.",n3t="see documentation",r3t="What can I sell?",o3t="What payment methods are supported?",i3t="What shipping methods are supported?",a3t="How do I connect an online store to my website?",s3t="How do I edit my online store?",l3t="You can sell physical and digital products, gift cards, and accept donations.",u3t="Subscriptions and appointments aren’t supported yet, but you can still offer them using third-party tools:",c3t="To start selling subscriptions, we recommend using Stripe. Just ask Horizons to help you connect it to your website.",d3t="For appointments, tools like Calendly work great. You can also ask Horizons how to add it to your site.",f3t="Choose from {0}, like cards, PayPal, Google Pay, Apple Pay, and others. Payment methods available for your store depend on where you’re selling, your location, currency, and who you’re selling to.",h3t="100+ payment methods",p3t="Once you connect an online store, you can define your shipping zones with up to 25 delivery options and set custom shipping rules based on order amount or item weight.",m3t="Click ‘Connect’ above and wait till Horizons sets it up for you.",g3t="Once the store’s connected, click ‘Integrations’ → ‘Online store’ to access all the online store settings.",v3t="You can manage your store anytime by clicking ‘Integrations’ → ‘Online store’.",b3t="Once it’s connected, you’ll see links that will redirect you to the built-in store manager. From there, you can manage products, payments, and more – without any prompting needed.",y3t="If you want to edit the way your online store looks (like the layout of your product list), just ask AI in the chat to make changes.",w3t="Connecting",E3t="Quick answers",C3t="Preview",_3t="Edit text",A3t="Code",D3t="Data",S3t="Discard",k3t="Save",x3t="Code changes saved.",T3t="You have unsaved changes.",I3t="Code changes couldn't be saved. Try saving again.",O3t="Saving changes...",R3t="Select file to edit",M3t="Save or discard code changes to exit the code editor.",L3t="Save or discard code changes to send the message.",F3t="Disable 'Select and edit' to change modes.",P3t="Feature roadmap",N3t="Ask Kodee",B3t=`Hi, I’m Kodee, your AI assistant.
